ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 199, Newfoundland and Labrador
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 199 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of NEWFOUNDLAND AND LABRADOR, with respect to the HEAVY RAINFALL from the remnants of Hurricane "Matthew", that affected the province from October 9 to October 11, 2016.
